async function openStackFrameInEditor(stackFrame, projectRoot) {
  const {
    fileName,
    lineNumber,
    column
  } = stackFrame;
  if (!fileName || !lineNumber) {
    _cliTools().logger.debug('Cannot open stack frame in editor');

  }
